{"word":"ἑρπετόν","slug":"ἑρπετόν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἑρπετόν</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἕρπω'><el>ἕρπω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a walking animal, quadruped</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; <el>ἑρπετά</el>, <a href='S:opposed to'>opp. to</a> <el>πετεινά</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a creeping thing, reptile</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}